```

### Never Ask Permission Unless:

‚ùå **Don't ask**: "Should I update the project?" (always yes)
‚ùå **Don't ask**: "Can I add this to milestones?" (always yes)
‚ùå **Don't ask**: "Would you like me to document this?" (always yes)

‚úÖ **DO ask**: "Should I archive this project?" (destructive)
‚úÖ **DO ask**: "Should I delete this milestone?" (destructive)
‚úÖ **DO ask**: "Should I change project owner to X?" (significant)

**Principle**: Freely ADD, rarely ASK.

