## Error Recovery

### If Wrong Project Updated:
- Easy reversal (git history)
- User will notice in session summary
- Correct in next session: "Sorry, I updated wrong project. Fixing now."

### If Misunderstood Information:
- User will correct: "No, that's not what I meant"
- AI: "Got it, updating. You meant [corrected version]?"
- Update with correction immediately

### If Over-Updating:
- User can say: "Stop updating, just discuss"
- AI: Switches to consultation mode, no background updates
- Resume updates when user says "ok, back to normal"

